experiment MARE
instrument HEA
start 2012 02 11 1930
end 2012 02 11 2330
status R
description HF radar measurements of enhanced plasma waves in aurora
contact Andrew Senior
email a.senior@lancaster.ac.uk
operator Mike Rietveld
submitter Andrew Senior
resources UK(18)
notes
The HF facility will be operated in radar mode to detect possible enhanced plasma 
waves in 
the aurora. The experiment will be cancelled if there is insufficient auroral 
activity.

